\prime }$
\end_inset

, there are asset profiles 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ b_{i,-1}^{\prime }\right\} _{i}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ b_{i,-1}^{\prime \prime }\right\} _{i}$
\end_inset

 such that equilibrium allocations starting from 
\begin_inset Formula $\left( \left\{ b_{i,-1}^{\prime }\right\}
_{i},B_{-1}^{\prime }\right) $
\end_inset

 and from 
\begin_inset Formula $\left( \left\{ b_{i,-1}^{\prime
\prime }\right\} _{i},B_{-1}^{\prime \prime }\right) $
\end_inset

 are the same. 
