\end_inset

These asset profiles satisfy
\begin_inset Formula \begin{equation*}
b_{i,-1}^{\prime }-b_{1,-1}^{\prime }=b_{i,-1}^{\prime \prime
}-b_{1,-1}^{\prime \prime }\text{ for all }i.
\end{equation*}
\end_inset


\begin_inset ERT
