	filename plots/comp_statics.pdf
	width 69text%

\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Caption Standard

\begin_layout Standard
Steady state level of government assets as a function of its redistribute motives. The x-axis plots 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha$
\end_inset

 with higher 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha$
\end_inset

's corresponding to more regressive planners
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

